d.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDamages%20in%20the%20case%20will%20be%20decided%20at%20a%20later%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20on%20Friday%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20complaints%20about%20bots%20on%20Twitter%20ahead%20of%20his%20purchase%20of%20the%20site%20were%20intentionally%20misleading%20to%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20in%20Musk's%20San%20Francisco%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-decoy-tesla-distracted-photographers-twitter-trial-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecurities%20fraud%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20unanimously%20found%20him%20liable%20for%20making%20two%20misleading%20statements%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20his%202022%20acquisition%20of%20the%20social%20media%20site.%20They%20rejected%20two%20other%20fraud%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20calculated%20how%20much%20Musk's%20complaints%20about%20bots%20on%20Twitter%20affected%20the%20company's%20share%20price%20before%20his%20acquisition%2C%20tracking%20five%20months%20of%20stock%20activity%20that%20showed%20a%20steep%20drop%20off%20after%20his%20comments.%20The%20jury%20found%20that%20Musk's%20remarks%20were%20intended%20to%20lower%20the%20company's%20value%20to%20secure%20a%20better%20deal%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-to-buy-twitter-board-accepts-44-billion-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%2444%20billion%20takeover%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%2C%20brought%20by%20former%20Twitter%20shareholders%2C%20was%20filed%20in%20October%202022.%20After%20a%20three-week%20trial%2C%20the%20jury%20deliberated%20for%20about%20three%20days%20before%20reaching%20its%20decision.%20Lawyers%20for%20Musk%20are%20expected%20to%20appeal%20the%20finding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonte%20Mann%2C%20business%20litigation%20partner%20and%20trial%20lawyer%20at%20the%20law%20firm%20Armstrong%2