l%20funding.%20Investors%20tended%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20more%20capital-intensive%20models%20because%20it's%20been%20hard%20to%20gauge%20when%20(or%20if)%20escape%20velocity%20shows%20up.%20This%20has%20traditionally%20been%20a%20tougher%20path%20than%20the%20%26quot%3Beasy%20button%26quot%3B%20of%20software%20and%20consumer%20internet%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that's%20changing%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20this%20changing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20driving%20a%20couple%20of%20structural%20shifts.%20First%2C%20it's%20accelerating%20and%20materially%20improving%20digital%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20across%20white-collar%20service%20work%20%E2%80%94%20as%20LLMs%20continue%20to%20advance.%20Second%2C%20that%20capability%20is%20starting%20to%20move%20into%20the%20physical%20world%2C%20where%20historically%20analog%20environments%20can%20now%20be%20digitized%20through%20progress%20in%20areas%20like%20VLA%20(video%2C%20language%2C%20action)%20models%2C%20world%20models%20(which%20simulate%20and%20help%20systems%20understand%20how%20the%20physical%20world%20works)%2C%20and%20embodied%20AI.%20The%20punchline%3A%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20AI%20is%20making%20physical%20industries%20meaningfully%20programmable%20%E2%80%94%20opening%20the%20door%20for%20faster%20scaling%20with%20less%20capital%20and%20labor%2C%20and%20starting%20to%20flip%20the%20dynamic%20in%20question%20%231%20on%20its%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20is%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20produce%20a%20lot%20more%20digital%20content%2C%20potentially%20denting%20the%20value.%20Meanwhile%2C%20physical%20things%20are%20still%20hard%2C%20so%20those%20could%20retain%20their%20value.%20Do%20you%20subscribe%20to%20this%20view%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20agree%20with%20your%20premise.%20Marc%20Andreessen%20famously%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSoftware%20is%20eating%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20Now%20AI%20is%20eating%20software%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20why%20you're%20seeing%20pressure%20on%20SaaS%20in%20the%20public%20markets.%20But%20in%20physical%20industries%2C%20you%20still%20must%20build%20and%20operate%20real%20things.%20AI%20can't%20fully%20replace%20the%20way%20it%20can%20take%20over%20a%20call%20center%2C%20act%20as%20a%20coding%20agent%2C%20or%20turn%20a%20novice%20into%20a%20capable%20designer%20by%20abstracting%20away%20skill.%20And%20that%20dynamic%20is%20now%20extending%20into%20legal%2C%20accounting%2C%20finance%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20nowhere%20to%20hide.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20punchline%3A%20in%20physical%20industries%20%E2%80%94%20manufacturing%2C%20logistics%2C%20energy%2C%20defense%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20is%20a%20powerful%20complement.%20It%20makes%20things%20faster%2C%20cheaper%2C%20less%20capital-intensive%2C%20and%20ultimately%20drives%20better%20returns.%20But%20it's%20not%20a%20full%20replacement%20in%20the%20way%20it%20will%20be%20across%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20service%20economy.%20I'm%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20this%20thesis%20based%20on%20what%20I'm%20seeing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20a%20big%20reason%20I%20left%20T.%20Rowe%20to%20come%20to%20Eclipse.%20You're%20already%20seeing%20it%20play%20out%20in%20real%20outcomes%20with%20companies%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'd%20add%20Anduril%20to%20that%20list.%20My%20bet%20is%20there%20are%20many%20more%20coming%2C%20and%20that%20capital%20that%20once%20flowed%20primarily%20into%20software%20and%20consumer%20internet%20will%20increasingly%20shift%20in%20this%20direction%20over%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20examples%20are%20you%20seeing%20in%20the%20market%2C%20or%20within%20Eclipse's%20portfolio%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sample%20size%20is%20growing%20quickly.%20I%20mentioned%20some%20of%20the%20household%20names%20in%20%233%2C%20and%20we're%20seeing%20many%20of%20the%20same%20dynamics%20across%20our%20own%20portfolio.%20A%20few%20examples%3A%20Wayve%2C%20Anduril%2C%20True%20Anomaly%2C%20Redwood%20Materials%2C%20Mytra%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20earlier-stage%20names%20like%20Mind%2C%20Matter%2C%20and%20BotCo.%20And%20then%20you%20have%20the%20%26quot%3Bpicks%20and%20shovels%26quot%3B%20layer%20powering%20the%20buildout%20of%20more%20advanced%20AGI%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ultimately%20ASI%20%E2%80%94%20capabilities%2C%20with%20companies%20like%20Cerebras%2C%20Oxide%2C%20and%20Tenstorrent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAny%20new%20investments%20you're%20making%20that%20fit%20into%20this%20broad%20thesis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMentioned%20several%20in%20%234%2C%20but%20at%20a%20high-level%2C%20Eclipse's%20focus%20areas%20remain%20general-purpose%20robotics%2C%20defense%20tech%2C%20next-gen%20manufacturing%2C%20semiconductors%20and%20next-gen%20compute%2C%20energy%20and%20batteries%2C%20and%20autonomy.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we're%20constantly%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Blook%20around%20corners%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20pressure-testing%20new%20theses%20and%20deciding%20where%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20invest%20or%20even%20build%20from%20scratch.%20That%20includes%20areas%20like%20fusion%2C%20water%2C%20space%2C%20world%20model%20builders%2C%20workforce%20development%20for%20the%20skilled%20trades%2C%20and%20neuromorphic%20computing%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20might%20this%20thesis%20go%20wrong%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhysical%20industries%20aren't%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20not%20just%20solving%20a%20technical%20or%20engineering%20problem%2C%20you%20then%20must%20scale%20it.%20And%20when%20you're%20physically%20building%20things%2C%20scaling%20well%20is%20incredibly%20hard.%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20talked%20about%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Bproduction%20hell%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20very%20real.%20Even%20with%20AI%20helping%20accelerate%20and%20improve%20execution%2C%20finding%20enough%20smart%2C%20capable%20people%20to%20do%20this%20at%20a%20high%20level%20is%20still%20a%20challenge.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20these%20businesses%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20capital%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20growing%20wave%20of%20entrepreneurs%20entering%20the%20space%20%E2%80%94%20so%20capital%20allocation%20really%20matters.%20You%20need%20to%20back%20the%20right%20outcomes%3A%20Defensible%2C%20high-impact%20ideas%2C%20exceptional%20founders%20who%20can%20attract%20top%20talent%2C%20and%20teams%20that%20can%20scale.%20Lastly%2C%20while%20the%20AI%20and%20geopolitical%20shifts%20feel%20durable%2C%20it's%20worth%20acknowledging%20the%20counterfactual.%20If%20global%20relations%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20%E2%80%94%20were%20to%20materially%20improve%2C%20you%20could%20see%20some%20slowing%20in%20re-shoring%20and%20the%20push%20to%20digitize%20physical%20industries%2C%20with%20a%20partial%20reversion%20to%20lower-cost%2C%20analog%20production%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-interview-atoms-bits-eclipse-joe-fath-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774042932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bda499e98a37a4841f22aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-interview-atoms-bits-eclipse-joe-fath-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eclipse's