https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-metaverse-crypto-blockchain-gaming-vr-real-estate-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emetaverse%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20fitting%20because%20%26quot%3Bleg%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20first%20part%20of%20the%20word%20%3Cem%3Elegacy%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-metaverse-legs-motion-capture-animation-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eabsence%20of%20legs%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20end%20up%20being%20the%20longest-lasting%20legacy%20of%20Meta's%20failed%20metaverse%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHear%20me%20out%3A%20This%20is%20a%20bad%20thing.%20We%20should%20all%20mourn%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-vr-metaverse-reality-labs-cuts-sadness-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emetaverse%20didn't%20work%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20future%20of%20the%20internet%20because%20the%20thing%20that%20ended%20up%20replacing%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20AI%20slopiverse%20%E2%80%94%20is%20far%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20rumors%20of%20the%20metaverse's%20death%20are%20somewhat%20exaggerated%20%E2%80%94%20Horizon%20Worlds%2C%20the%20main%20metaverse%20experience%20owned%20and%20operated%20by%20Meta%2C%20will%20continue%20on%20as%20a%20mobile%20game.%20After%20fan%20response%20to%20the%20announcement%20that%20it%20would%20shut%20down%20the%20VR%20version%2C%20Meta%20announced%20it%20would%20keep%20it%20up.%20There%20are%20still%20games%20out%20there%20for%20the%20Quest%20headset%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20metaverse%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20concept%20of%20a%20digital%20place%20where%20your%20avatar%20can%20spend%20real%20money%20on%20fake%20digital%20items%20thrives%20(for%20better%20or%20worse)%20on%20Roblox.%20Meta%20CTO%20Andrew%20Bosworth%2C%20who%20previously%20ran%20the%20VR%2FAR%20division%2C%20posted%20to%20Threads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-text-post-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.com%2F%40boztank%2Fpost%2FDWFPo-0ged4%5C%22%20data-text-post-version%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.com%2F%40boztank%2Fpost%2FDWFPo-0ged4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20View%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20actually%20spent%20some%20time%20in%20Horizon%20Worlds%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20and%20I%20can%20confirm%20that%20it%20sucked.%20Most%20of%20the%20other%20users%20I%20encountered%20seemed%20to%20be%20children%20(based%20on%20their%20voices)%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20deeply%20uncomfortable%20as%20an%20adult%20talking%20to%20strange%20kids%20without%20their%20parents%20knowing%2C%20and%20my%20own%20real%20identity%20was%20obscured.%20It%20was%20also%20just%20%E2%80%A6%20boring.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20these%20strangers%2C%20and%20there%20wasn't%20much%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo.%26quot%3B%20I%20spent%20some%20time%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bcomedy%20club%26quot%3B%20where%20users%20could%20sign%20up%20to%20go%20onstage%20like%20an%20open%20mic%20night.%20It%20may%20not%20surprise%20you%20that%20there%20wasn't%20much%20comedy%20happening%3B%20the%20stage%20was%20often%20taken%20over%20by%20what%20sounded%20like%20an%208-year-old%20kid%20who%20just%20wanted%20to%20sing%20Taylor%20Swift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20metaverse%20was%20always%20a%20punchline%20and%20a%20joke.%20Its%20product%20demos%20were%20likely%20among%20the%20most%20humiliating%20moments%20for%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzuckerberg-sweat-armpit-hair-blow-dry-big-events-new-book-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esweated%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20his%20T-shirt%20onstage.%20It%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2Fmetaverse-facebook-mark-zuckerberg-memes-1849708985%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememe%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20bad%20this%20whole%20thing%20looked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20everyone%20thought%20this%20looked%20corny%20and%20bad%2C%20just%20like%20most%20everyone%20thought%20NFTs%20looked%20scammy%20and%20bad%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20quite%20happy%20now%20that%20we%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20right.%20That's%20partly%20because%20it%20feels%20good%20to%20be%20right%2C%20but%20partly%20%E2%80%94%20for%20those%20who%20are%20highly%20skeptical%20of%20the%20tech%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20out%20of%20a%20deluded%20idea%20that%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20dud%2C%20just%20like%20NFTs%20and%20the%20metaverse.%20But%20that%20last%20part%20isn't%20true%3B%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20happen.%20(It%20already%20is!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20actually%20why%20you%20should%20feel%20sad%20the%20metaverse%20didn't%20work%20out.%20It%20was%20actually%20a%20beautiful%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20a%20vision%20of%20the%20internet%20based%20on%20human%20connection%20and%20wholesome%20leisure%20activities%20like%20going%20to%20a%20comedy%20club%20or%20playing%20a%20video%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20did%20we%20get%20instead%20of%20that%3F%20We%20have%20the%20internet%20we're%20stuck%20on%20now%2C%20full%20of%20misery%20and%20sloppified%20out%20the%20wazoo.%20Did%20you%20know%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhorizon.meta.com%2Fevent%2F1150252113839760%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColdplay%3C%2Fa%3E%20played%20a%20concert%20in%20Horizon%20Worlds%3F%20Of%20course%20not%20because%20it%20didn't%20lead%20to%20a%20weekslong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoldplay-concert-ceo-kiss-cam-questions-why-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20pile-on%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20two%20concert%20attendees%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20shown%20on%20the%20Jumbotron.%20Would've%