20across%20both%20platforms%20and%20acting%20early%20can%20be%20key%20to%20finding%20the%20best%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276cfaff1-1e7f-4ff6-870a-cbd1db7fb554%5C%22%3EWhen%20did%20BTS%20tickets%20go%20on%20sale%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETickets%20for%20BTS'%20world%20tour%20were%20released%20in%20stages%2C%20beginning%20with%20exclusive%20fan%20access%20before%20opening%20to%20the%20general%20public.%20The%20first%20window%20was%20the%20ARMY%20Membership%20presale%2C%20which%20ran%20on%20January%2022%20and%20January%2023%2C%202026.%20Fans%20who%20registered%20on%20Weverse%20and%20verified%20their%20membership%20in%20advance%20received%20early%20access%20codes%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20purchase%20tickets%20before%20wider%20demand.%20This%20presale%20was%20especially%20competitive%20in%20major%20markets%2C%20with%20many%20stadium%20dates%20seeing%20large%20portions%20of%20inventory%20claimed%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20presales%2C%20general%20public%20ticket%20sales%20officially%20began%20on%20January%2024%2C%202026%2C%20via%20primary%20ticketing%20partners%20including%20Ticketmaster%20and%20Live%20Nation.%20Once%20tickets%20went%20on%20sale%20to%20everyone%2C%20demand%20surged%20quickly%2C%20and%20many%20shows%20either%20sold%20out%20or%20became%20extremely%20limited%20the%20same%20day.%20After%20that%20point%2C%20remaining%20inventory%20and%20additional%20availability%20largely%20shifted%20to%20verified%20resale%20marketplaces%2C%20which%20is%20where%20many%20fans%20turned%20if%20they%20missed%20the%20initial%20on%E2%80%91sale%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESee%20more%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftickets%2Fstubhub-review-fees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIs%20StubHub%20legit%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftickets%2Fwhere-to-buy-harry-styles-tickets-concert-tour%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarry%20Styles%20tickets%3