alled%20Life%20Burns%20Faster%20with%20multiple%20dates%20in%20October%2C%20already%20sold%20out%20on%20Metallica's%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMetallica%20formed%20in%201981%20and%20became%20a%20foundational%20force%20in%20thrash%20metal%2C%20eventually%20growing%20into%20one%20of%20the%20most%20commercially%20successful%20heavy%20bands%20ever.%20Their%20classic%20run%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BKill%20'Em%20All%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BRide%20the%20Lightning%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMaster%20of%20Puppets%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%E2%80%A6And%20Justice%20for%20All%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20set%20the%20template%20for%20modern%20metal%2C%20while%20Metallica%20(aka%20The%20Black%20Album)%20made%20them%20a%20mainstream%20stadium%20draw%20with%20songs%20like%20%26quot%3BEnter%20Sandman.%26quot%3B%20Today's%20lineup%3A%20James%20Hetfield%2C%20Lars%20Ulrich%2C%20Kirk%20Hammett%2C%20and%20Robert%20Trujillo%2C%20is%20still%20built%20for%20big%20live%20shows%2C%20and%20the%20M72%20era%20has%20leaned%20into%20the%20band's%20%26quot%3Bno%20repeat%26quot%3B%20weekend%20approach%20(different%20setlists%20across%20multiple%20nights)%2C%20which%20keeps%20even%20repeat%20attendees%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETicket%20availability%20depends%20on%20the%20date%20and%20location.%20Some%20European%20shows%20still%20have%20standard%20tickets%20available%2C%20but%20most%20VIP%20options%20are%20sold%20out.%20If%20your%20preferred%20night%20is%20sold%20out%20on%20the%20primary%20market%2C%20fans%20typically%20turn%20to%20verified%20resale%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118283907o1-20%26h%3D1e71bf01239d1e3c4f3a7a275b6fe1efbabe02dbce0ea867b53e27fc395fd3b0%26postID%3D69bda73fd097316b35d79950%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftickets%252Fwhere-to-buy-metallica-tickets-concert-tour-residency%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.stubhub.com%252Fmetallica-tickets%252Fperformer%252F8147%5C%22%20data-autoaffili