onthly%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118282595pp-20%26h%3D7e0ef3d482acb0967b938e4b0cf9ed11f3292de012ff47ab7bb5d6d5ad7c5171%26postID%3D69bd91db7a1e7b24a6e469b0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fdeals%252Fnordvpn-deal-2026-3%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.jdoqocy.com%252Fclick-6415797-13382109%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20all%20NordVPN%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20even%20deeper%20discount%20on%20two-year%20plans%2C%20with%20savings%20ranging%20from%2070%25%20to%2074%25%20compared%20to%20what%20you'd%20pay%20after%20two%20years%20on%20a%20month-to-month%20plan.%20A%20two-year%20Basic%20plan%20costs%20%2481.36%20up%20front%2C%20which%20shakes%20out%20to%20about%20%243.39%20a%20month.%20In%20contrast%2C%20monthly%20Basic%20plans%20go%20for%20%2412.99%20a%20month.%20Subscriptions%20will%20renew%20at%20their%20then-standard%20prices%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20term%20period%20unless%20canceled%20before%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20prices%20and%20discount%20percentages%20are%20for%20US%20customers%2C%20but%20similar%20deals%20are%20available%20in%20other%20regions%20around%20the%20world.%20Customers%20can%20find%20applicable%20pricing%20and%20currency%20for%20their%20country%20by%20navigating%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118282595pp-20%26h%3D7e0ef3d482acb0967b938e4b0cf9ed11f3292de012ff47ab7bb5d6d5ad7c5171%26postID%3D69bd91db7a1e7b24a6e469b0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fdeals%252Fnordvpn-deal-2026-3%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.jdoqocy.com%252Fclick-6415797-13382109%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENordVPN%20landing%20page%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20limited-time%20deal%2C%20customers%20in%20the%20US%20and%20select%20other%20countries%20can%20also%20earn%20a%20free%20Amazon%20gift%20card%20if%20they%20opt%20for%20a%20two-year%20plan%20on%20the%20Plus%20or%20higher%20tiers.%20The%20Amazon%20vouchers%20range%20from%20%2420%20to%20%2450%2C%20with%20larger%20amounts%20accompanying%20pricier%20plans.%20These%20Amazon%20digital%20gift%20cards%20will%20be%20sent%20between%20days%2031%20and%2050%20of%20service.%20The%20Amazon%20gift%20card%20deal%20is%20also%20available%20to%20customers%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVPNs%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20valuable%20cybersecurity%20tools%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age%2C%20and%20NordVPN%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20on%20the%20market.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20why%20we%20regularly%20recommend%20(and%20trust)%20the%20service%20in%20our%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fnordvpn-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENordVPN%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20app%20also%20has%20a%20handy%2030-day%20money-back%20guarantee%20if%20you%20find%20that%20it's%20not%20what%20you're%20looking%20for.%20Keep%20reading%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20service%2C%20the%20deal%2C%20and%20what%20you%20can%20find%20in%20each%20tier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a191c9a-ef48-425c-ae99-267df02148f5%5C%22%3EFAQ%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20claim%20the%20Amazon%20gift%20card%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you%20purchase%20a%20two-year%20plan%20on%20a%20Plus%20or%20higher%20tier%2C%20you'll%20receive%20an%20email%20with%20additional%20information%20on%20how%20to%20claim%20your%20gift%20card.%20The%20gift%20card%2C%20once%20claimed%2C%20will%20be%20emailed%20to%20you%20within%2031%20to%2050%20days%20after%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20an%20eligible%20NordVPN%20plan%20(once%20you're%20outside%20the%2030-day%20money-back%20guarantee%20window).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20NordVPN's%20four%20tiers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENordVPN%20offers%20four%20tiers%20of%20service%20in%20the%20US%3A%20Basic%2C%20Plus%2C%20Complete%2C%20and%20Prime.%20All%20of%20these%20plans%20are%20available%20in%20month-to-month%2C%20yearlong%2C%20and%20two-year-long%20contracts.%20Basic%20comes%20with%20NordVPN's%20standard%20VPN%20offerings%2C%20while%20Plus%20adds%20an%20ad%20and%20tracker%20blocker%2C%20password%20manager%2C%20and%20anti-malware%20and%20browsing%20protection%20through%20CrowdStrike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Complete%20plan%20offers%20all%20of%20this%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20email%2C%20credit%20card%2C%20and%20ID%20monitor%2C%20scam%20call%20protection%2C%20and%201%20TB%20of%20cloud%20storage.%20Prime%20is%20the%20cream%20of%20the%20crop.%20It%20includes%20everything%20we've%20outlined%20above%20and%20combines%20it%20with%20NordProtect%2C%20Nord's%20identity%20protection%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlan%20names%20and%20details%20vary%20slightly%20from%20region%20to%20region%20(in%20the%20UK%2C%20for%20example%2C%20there's%20an%20Ultimate%20tier)%2C%20so%20you%20should%20check%20to%20see%20the%20exact%20details%20in%20your%20country%20on%20the%20NordVPN%20landing%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20there%20any%20other%20VPN%20deals%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20interested%20in%20NordVPN%20but%20still%20shopping%20for%20a%20new%20VPN%20service%2C%20several%20other%20apps%20that%20we've%20tested%20are%20offering%20discounts%20right%20now.%20ExpressVPN%2C%20Surfshark%2C%20and%20ProtonVPN%20are%20among%20the%20top%20services%20with%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fbest-cheap-vpn-deals-from-top-tested-apps-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20cheap%20VPN%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fnordvpn-deal-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774038262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd928358b5806618e7cde3%3Fformat%3Dj