22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Frankie%20Paul's%20%26quot%3BBachelorette%26quot%3B%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20the%20Most%20Dramatic%20Season%20Ever.%20Now%2C%20it%20will%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20the%20Most%20Dramatic%20Season%20to%20Never%20Exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20cast%2031-year-old%20Paul%2C%20a%20TikToker%20and%20the%20star%20of%20Hulu's%20hit%20reality%20series%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-frankie-paul-mayci-neeley-mormon-wives-interview-business-influencing-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Secret%20Lives%20of%20Mormon%20Wives%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20next%20Bachelorette%20was%20framed%20as%20a%20groundbreaking%20change%20of%20pace%20for%20the%20famously%20risk-averse%20juggernaut.%20The%20long-running%20franchise's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbachelor-franchise-less-popular-rise-and-fall-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eratings%20have%20been%20in%20steady%20decline%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20late%202010s%2C%20so%20things%20were%20finally%20dire%20enough%20to%20cast%20their%20first%20lead%20from%20outside%20the%20franchise.%20Enter%20Paul%2C%20a%20messy%20single%20mom%20whose%20exploits%20on%20%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20had%20already%20buoyed%20ABC's%20Disney-owned%20sister%20network%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Fthe-secret-lives-of-mormon-wives-hulu-streaming-viewership-popularity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord-breaking%20ratings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20surprisingly%20big%20swing%20for%20the%20network%20that%20was%20praised%20for%20promising%20to%20breathe%20new%20life%20into%20the%20franchise.%20But%20when%20you%20swing%20that%20big%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20whiff%20spectacularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20happened%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20when%20the%20network%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20pull%20the%20plug%20on%20Paul's%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette%26quot%3B%20amid%20a%20police%20investigation%20into%20a%20February%20incident%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-frankie-paul-dakota-mortensen-allegations-bachelorette-controversy-explained-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealleged%20domestic%20violence%20between%20Paul%20and%20her%20ex%2C%20Dakota%20Mortensen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20leak%20of%20a%20disturbing%20video%20from%20Paul's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-frankie-paul-mormon-momtok-influencer-arrested-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20reported%20altercation%20with%20Mortensen%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENever%20mind%20the%20gauntlets%20of%20already-completed%20press%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Ftv%2Ftv-news%2Finside-the-bachelorette-season-22-cancellation-taylor-frankie-paul-1236541439%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%20%248.2%20million%20in%20TV%20promos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20season%20had%20already%20wrapped%20filming%20and%20was%20set%20to%20premiere%20in%20three%20days'%20time.%20The%20dream%20was%20over%20for%20Paul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20it's%20time%20the%20dream%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette%26quot%3B%20is%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea2e1274-264e-4c2f-aa76-cdab9662b480%5C%22%3ECasting%20Taylor%20Frankie%20Paul%20was%20always%20going%20to%20be%20risky%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20suit%20sits%20on%20a%20couch%20next%20to%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20white%20dress%20who's%20wiping%20away%20tears.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd814a5b58f1f0f9335a67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDakota%20Mortensen%20and%20Taylor%20Frankie%20Paul's%20off-and-on%20relationship%20has%20been%20chronicles%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Secret%20Lives%20of%20Mormon%20Wives.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EFred%20Hayes%2FDisney%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChaos%20has%20always%20been%20Paul's%20brand.%20Before%20Paul%20was%20poised%20to%20be%20the%20star%20of%20not%20one%20but%20two%20television%20shows%2C%20she%20was%20the%20self-destructive%20and%20eminently%20watchable%20leader%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-secret-lives-of-mormon-wives-cast-social-media-account-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMomTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20loose%20collection%20of%20Mormon%20moms%20who%20make%20TikToks%20together%20in%20Utah.%20Though%20the%20women%20gained%20followings%20for%20their%20perfect%20barrel%20curls%20and%20silly%20dancing%20videos%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpert-explains-soft-swinging-how-the-mormon-momtok-drama-unfolded-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebombshell%202022%20video%20of%20Paul%20admitting%20to%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20swinging%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20other%20members%20of%20MomTok%20and%20their%20husbands%20that%20catapulted%20her%20and%20her%20circle%20of%20friends%20to%20infamy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20got%20them%20a%20Hulu%20reality%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHulu%20learned%20early%20in%20filming%20%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20very%20qualities%20that%20made%20Paul%20a%20compelling%20reality-television%20character%20would%20also%20make%20her%20a%20liability.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20show%20paused%20production%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sltrib.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F02%2F28%2Fmormon-mom-tiktok-star-taylor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaul%20was%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20an%20altercation%20with%20Mortensen%20and%20was%20charged%20with%20aggravated%20assault%2C%20child%20abuse%2C%20and%20domestic%20violence%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20child.%20She%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20the%20aggravated%20assault%20charge%20%E2%80%94%20a%20third-degree%20felony%20%E2%80%94%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20other%20charges%20being%20dropped%2C%20and%20entered%20a%20plea%20of%20abeyance%20for%2036%20months%2C%20after%20which%20time%20the%20charge%20would%20be%20lessened%20to%20a%20misdemeanor%20if%20she%20abided%20by%20the%20terms%20of%20her%20probation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20chronicles%20this%20incident%20in%20its%20very%20first%20episode%2C%20airing%20police%20bodycam%20footage%20of%20a%20distraught%20Paul%20being%20arrested%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Utah.%20The%20next%20episode%20picks%20up%20a%20year%20later%2C%20with%20Paul%20pregnant%20with%20Mortensen's%20child%20and%20the%20couple%20back%20together.%20(Their%20child%2C%20Ever%20True%2C%20was%20born%20in%20March%202024.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20show's%20four%20seasons%2C%20Paul%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20compelling%2C%20frustrating%2C%20and%20mesmerizing%20characters%20on%20reality%20television.%20She%20takes%20the%20arrest%20and%20subsequent%20therapy%20and%20treatment%20hard%2C%20sobbing%20onscreen%20in%20moments%20that%20feel%20too%20private%20to%20be%20broadcast%20to%20the%20world.%20She%20repeatedly%20admits%20to%20being%20at%20fault%20in%20the%202023%20incident%20in%20interviews%20and%20on%20%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20prostrates%20herself%20so%20deeply%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20accountability%20that%20she%20can%20only%20counterbalance%20it%20by%20doing%20something%20so%20self-destructive%20%E2%80%94%20posting%20shady%20TikToks%20about%20her%20friends%2C%20sleeping%20with%20Mortensen%20the%20night%20before%20leaving%20to%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20that%20she's%20forced%20to%20repeat%20the%20cycle%20anew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20all%20to%20say%20that%20ABC%20should%20have%20seen%20this%20coming.%20The%20fact%20that%20they%20didn't%20or%20couldn't%20course-correct%20in%20time%20underscores%20the%20Bachelor%20Nation's%20Achilles'%20heel%3A%20inflexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222508%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Secret%20Lives%20of%20Mormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20featuring%20Dakota%20Mortensen%20in%20a%20plaid%20brown%20shirt%20and%20brown%20pants%20hugging%20his%20partner%20Taylor%20Frankie%20Paul%2C%20who%20is%20in%20a%20brown%20dress%2C%20while%20they%20sit%20on%20two%20green%20chairs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e193cc83b8099cf9fd7229%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221881%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDakota%20Mortensen%20and%20Taylor%20Frankie%20Paul%20have%20been%20dating%20for%20two%20years.%3Cp%3EFred%20Hayes%20%2F%20Disney%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20over%2050%20seasons%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette%26quot%3B%20combined%2C%20plus%20dozens%20more%20spinoffs%2C%20the%20franchise%20has%20done%20precious%20little%20to%20evolve%20as%20the%20pool%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freality-dating-shows-stream-netflix-hulu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereality%20dating%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20increasingly%20crowded.%20Its%20efforts%20to%20increase%20racial%20diversity%20among%20the%20cast%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbachelor-rachael-kirkconnell-matt-james-complete-timeline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebackfired%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bustle.com%2Fp%2Flee-apologizes-for-his-racist-tweets-on-the-bachelorette-men-tell-all-but-only-after-deflecting-for-most-of-the-episode-73745%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%3C%2Fa%3E%20times%2C%20and%20its%20format%20of%20dates%20and%20rose%20ceremonies%20has%20remained%20almost%20entirely%20unchanged%20over%20two%20decades.%20A%20change%20in%20showrunners%20and%20a%20new%20aesthetic%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbachelor-in-paradise-season-10-cast-premiere-date-trailer-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10th%20season%20of%20the%20spinoff%20%26quot%3BBachelor%20in%20Paradise%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20caused%20a%20minor%20stir%2C%20mostly%20serving%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20just%20how%20stale%20the%20flagship%20series%20has%20become%20by%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20promo%20material%20that%20boasted%20Paul's%20%26quot%3BBachelorette%26quot%3B%20season%20would%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20the%20mold%2C%26quot%3B%20ABC%20dropped%20their%20star%20the%20moment%20her%20signature%20brand%20of%20chaos%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20her%20previously%20known%202023%20arrest%2C%20which%20acts%20as%20part%20of%20her%20origin%20story%20on%20season%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20became%20a%20drawback%20to%20the%20network%20instead%20of%20a%20selling%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20you%20think%20of%20the%20leaked%20video%2C%20of%20Paul%20and%20Mortensen's%20relationship%20dynamic%2C%20and%20whether%20either%20of%20them%20should%20have%20a%20platform%20or%20be%20on%20reality%20television%20while%20both%20openly%20battling%20issues%20with%20addiction%20and%20mental%20health%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette%26quot%3B%20tried%20and%20failed%20to%20have%20it%20both%20ways.%20The%20most%20frustrating%20part%20is%20that%20the%20franchise%20may%20learn%20the%20wrong%20lesson%20from%20the%20fiasco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282792b18-def1-4add-974a-b3d302d4aac3%5C%22%3E'The%20Bachelor'%20franchise%20needs%20to%20stop%20pretending%20its%20leads%20are%20role%20models%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20red%20dress%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20a%20stained%20glass%20window%20holding%20a%20book%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BTHE%20BOOK%20OF%20MORE%20MEN.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd82165b58f1f0f9335a6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaylor%20Frankie%20Paul's%20Bachelorette%20promo%20photos%20leaned%20into%20her%20Mormon%20background.%3Cp%3EDisney%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20moment%20a%20gaggle%20of%20women%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20limo%20in%20the%20series'%20groundbreaking%202002%20premiere%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelor%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20committed%20to%20selling%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20romantic%20fairy%20tale.%20Red%20roses%20are%20currency%20toward%20earning%20the%20man%20or%20woman%20of%20your%20dreams.%20Contestants%20talk%20about%20meeting%20the%20love%20of%20their%20life%2C%20of%20the%20engagement%20they've%20been%20dreaming%20of%20since%20they%20were%20little%20girls.%20Overnight%20dates%20are%20still%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BFantasy%20Suites.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20two-plus%20decades%20of%20competitive%20romance%20have%20softened%20some%20of%20the%20franchise's%20buzzwords%20into%20meta-commentary%20on%20the%20show%20itself%20(who%20is%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ehere%20for%20the%20right%20reasons%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B)%2C%20the%20show's%20operating%20principle%20still%20rests%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20its%20lead%20is%20the%20most%20perfect%20person%20worthy%20of%20%26quot%3Bfinding%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20casting%20a%20complex%2C%20deeply%20flawed%20woman%20as%20a%20romantic%20lead%20was%20inspired%20and%20would%20no%20doubt%20have%20made%20for%20a%20compelling%20season%20of%20television.%20But%20the%20show%20chose%20Paul%20without%20considering%20the%20shackles%20it%20would%20inherently%20place%20on%20her.%20Bachelor%20Nation%20viewers%20still%20expect%20leads%20to%20be%20unimpeachable%20role%20models%20%E2%80%94%20Taylor%20Frankie%20Paul%20was%20a%20fascinating%20choice%20because%20she%20got%20famous%20precisely%20because%20she%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20this%20leaves%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette%2C%26quot%3B%20ABC%2C%20Paul%2C%20Mortensen%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20cast%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20Disney%20Entertainment%2C%20Paul%2C%20and%20Mortensen%20have%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-frankie-paul-dakota-mortensen-allegations-bachelorette-controversy-explained-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereleased%20statements%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20emphasize%20they%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bfocusing%20on%20family%26quot%3B%20amid%20the%20news%3B%20filming%20for%20the%20fifth%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20is%20currently%20on%20pause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20dust%20settles%20in%20Hollywood%20and%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20Paul%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20only%20one%20doing%20some%20repenting.%20Scrapping%20the%20season%20shouldn't%20teach%20ABC%20brass%20that%20risks%20aren't%20worth%20taking.%20It%20should%20show%20them%20that%20if%20they're%20going%20to%20shake%20up%20the%20franchise%2C%20they%20can't%20expect%20one%20woman's%20unpredictable%20personality%20to%20provide%20an%20advertiser-safe%20earthquake%20that%20will%20do%20the%20work%20of%20dozens%20of%20top%20producers%20and%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20franchise%20is%20going%20to%20stay%20afloat%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20find%20something%20new%2C%20entertaining%2C%20and%20poignant%20to%20say%20about%20modern%20dating%20and%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20happy%20ending.%20At%20one%20time%2C%20Paul's%20casting%20represented%20a%20chance%20to%20do%20exactly%20that.%20Pulling%20her%20season%20shows%20the%20network%20was%20more%20interested%20in%20juicing%20ratings%2C%20as%20long%20as%20the%20outcome%20wasn't%20as%20messy%20as%20its%20lead.%20Perhaps%20it's%20time%20to%20question%20if%20ABC%20cast%20her%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-taylor-frankie-paul-bachelorette-season-canceled-abc-risks-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774033874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd8102e98a37a4841f2154%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-taylor-frankie-paul-bachelorette-season-canceled-abc-risks-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20casting%20%26quot%3BMormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20star%20Taylor%20Frankie%20Paul%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette%2C%26quot%3B%20ABC%20tried%20and%20failed%20to%20have%20it%20both%20ways.%20They%20might%20learn%20the%20wrong%20lesson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Samantha%20Rollins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-taylor-frankie-paul-bachelorette-season-canceled-abc-risks-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BofA%20isn't%20ruling%20out%20a%20rate%20hike%20this%20year%2C%20and%20says%20it%20would%20take%203%20things%20for%20that%20to%20happen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20market%20floor%20on%20Wall%20Street%20during%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell's%20remarks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd721658b5806618e7cc87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJeenah%20Moon%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBank%20of%20America%20said%20clients%20have%20been%20asking%20about%20the%20risk%20of%20the%20Fed%20hiking%20rates%20in%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMarkets%20have%20priced%20in%20a%2012%25%20probability%20of%20a%20rate%20hike%20in%20April%2C%20up%20from%200%25%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20economists%20outlined%20three%20conditions%20under%20which%20the%20Fed%20might%20consider%20raising%20rates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20said%20clients%20have%20been%20asking%20whether%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20could%20shock%20markets%20and%20raise%20rates%20this%20year.%20The%20bank%20said%20it's%20not%20ruling%20it%20out%2C%20but%20some%20specific%20conditions%20would%20have%20to%20be%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20adjusted%20their%20expectations%20for%20where%20rates%20could%20go%20after%20Powell's%20hawkish%20remarks%20at%20the%20central%20bank's%20March%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20are%20pricing%20in%20a%2012%25%20probability%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20raise%20its%20benchmark%20rate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fmarkets%2Finterest-rates%2Fcme-fedwatch-tool.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECME%20FedWatch%20tool%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20up%20from%200%25%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20economists%20still%20believe%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20are%20more%20likely%20than%20hikes%20in%202026%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20oil%20shock%20from%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Iran%20subsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20%26quot%3Bsustained%20but%20moderate%26quot%3B%20impacts%20on%20the%20US%20economy%20from%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20increase%20the%20risks%20of%20a%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FXZk1x%2F4%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22429%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20flagged%20oil%20prices%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bsweet%20spot%26quot%3B%20for%20hikes%20is%20likely%20within%20the%20%2480-100%20range%20for%20US%20crude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20three%20conditions%20Bank%20of%20America%20said%20must%20be%20met%20for%20the%20Fed%20to%20seriously%20consider%20raising%20rates%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cb820be-29a4-4a9d-ad5a-a8ab9529e178%5C%22%3EA%20stable%20labor%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20walks%20past%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20on%20Wall%20Street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd73d358b5806618e7cca6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20condition%20for%20a%20potential%20Fed%20rate%20hike%2C%20in%20Bank%20of%20America's%20view%2C%20is%20a%20stable%20labor%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFed%20to%20consider%20hiking%20rates%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20confident%20first%20and%20foremost%20that%20the%20labor%20market%20is%20holding%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20said%20that%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20needs%20to%20stay%20below%204.5%25.%20The%20most%20recent%20jobs%20report%20showed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-report-february-data-live-updates-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunemployment%20ticked%20up%20to%204.4%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February.%20The%20US%20economy%20also%20recorded%20a%20surprise%20job%20loss%20during%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8982dab-e2ac-407b-a24c-09f841d55aaf%5C%22%3EFurther%20rise%20in%20inflation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225103%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Consumer%20prices%20rise%20making%20affordability%20concerns%20more%20pronounced.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd725c58b5806618e7cc8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERONALDO%20SCHEMIDT%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20said%20the%20Fed%20would%20need%20to%20see%20that%20the%20war%20in%20Iran%20is%20translating%20into%20higher%20core%20inflation%2C%20affecting%20more%20than%20just%20energy%20prices%2C%20before%20considering%20rate%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20explained%20that%20this%20could%20happen%20through%20higher%20energy%20prices%20raising%20input%20costs%20across%20the%20economy%2C%20a%20slow%20but%20sticky%20input%20for%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20possibility%20is%20that%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20from%20the%20conflict%20could%20cause%20price%20spikes%20unrelated%20to%20oil.%20Fertilizer%20and%20helium%20supply%20shocks%2C%20which%20could%20raise%20food%20prices%20and%20costs%20in%20the%20tech%20and%20healthcare%20sectors%2C%20are%20examples%20of%20this%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20said%20that%20the%20Fed%20may%20be%20able%20to%20justify%20overlooking%20inflation%20if%20it%20can%20be%20tied%20to%20tariffs%2C%20which%20they%20consider%20more%20transitory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22868cf0c9-8861-429b-82b1-38a4e72bbfd8%5C%22%3EPowell%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd740758b5806618e7ccad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrendan%20SMIALOWSKI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20condition%20for%20the%20Fed%20to%20consider%20raising%20rates%20this%20year%20is%20for%20Powell%20to%20still%20be%20Chairman%20of%20the%20centra%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20will%20preside%20over%20one%20more%20FOMC%20meeting%20before%20his%20term%20expires%20in%20May.%20Trump's%20nominee%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-warsh-next-fed-chair-stock-market-top-takeaways-investors-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKevin%20Warsh%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20need%20to%20be%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Senate%20before%20assuming%20the%20role%20ahead%20of%20the%20June%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20risks%20that%20Warsh's%20confirmation%20will%20be%20delayed%2C%20with%20Senator%20Thom%20Tillis%20of%20North%20Carolina%20stating%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthom-tillis-kevin-warsh-powell-fed-probe-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewon't%20confirm%20Warsh%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20legal%20investigation%20into%20Powell%20is%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20considers%20Powell%20a%20%26quot%3Bmoderate%20dove%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20%26quot%3Bwill%20prioritize%20the%20labor%20market%20over%20inflation%20if%20risks%20to%20the%20two%20are%20roughly%20balanced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20they%20think%20the%20bar%20for%20a%20rate%20hike%20will%20be%20demonstrably%20higher%20with%20Warsh%20as%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20said%20he%20will%20stay%20on%20as%20interim%20chair%20if%20a%20successor%20hasn't%20been%20confirmed%20by%20then%2C%20and%20has%20also%20indicated%20he'll%20remain%20a%20governor%20while%20the%20investigation%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-hike-powell-bofa-interest-markets-investors-powell-trump-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774033253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd81e9e98a37a4841f215d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-hike-powell-bofa-interest-markets-investors-powell-trump-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Markets%20are%20recalibrating%20expectations%20for%20Fed%20rate%20cuts.%20BofA%20says%20the%20Fed%20could%20possibly%20hike%20rates%20if%20three%20conditions%20are%20met.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nbuchanan%40insider.com%20(Naomi%20Buchanan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2