sters-sexual-abuse-lawsuit-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnnie%20Altman%20filed%20her%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20Missouri%20in%20January%202025.%20She%20alleged%20that%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20who%20is%20nine%20years%20older%20than%20her%2C%20sexually%20abused%20her%20between%201997%20and%202006%2C%20beginning%20when%20she%20was%20three%20years%20old%2C%20when%20they%20were%20growing%20up%20in%20Clayton%2C%20Missouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations.%20In%20a%20public%20statement%20following%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20he%2C%20his%20two%20younger%20brothers%2C%20and%20their%20mother%20said%20Annie%20Altman%20had%20%26quot%3Bmental%20health%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman's%20countersuit%20said%20that%20his%20sister%20made%20up%20the%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20%E2%80%94%20posting%20them%20on%20social%20media%20as%20well%20as%20including%20them%20in%20her%20lawsuit%20%E2%80%94%20after%20their%20family%20declined%20her%20%26quot%3Bdemands%20for%20unrestricted%20financial%20support%26quot%3B%20in%20light%20of%20her%20mental%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20only%20points%20of%20agreement%20in%20this%20case%20is%20that%20the%20claims%20are%20disturbing%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20so%20if%20they%20prove%20true%20but%20nonetheless%20unfortunate%20if%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Bluestone%20wrote%20in%20his%20Friday%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Mahoney%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20Annie%20Altman%2C%20said%20she%20plans%20to%20file%20a%20new%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Court's%20ruling%20relates%20to%20procedural%20matters%2C%20which%20have%20no%20bearing%20on%20the%20substance%20of%20Ann%20Altman's%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahoney%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Court%20granted%20leave%20for%20Ms.%20Altman%20to%20file%20an%20amended%20complaint%2C%20which%20we%20will%20do%20promptly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Sam%20Altman%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-sexual-abuse-lawsuit-sister-annie-defamation-countersuit-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774028891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd80e358b5806618e7cd22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-sexual-abuse-lawsuit-sister-annie-defamation-countersuit-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20federal%20judge%20greenlit%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman's%20defamation%20countersuit%20against%20his%20sister%2C%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-sexual-abuse-lawsuit-sister-annie-defamation-countersuit-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20days%20after%20chairman's%20exit%2C%20three%20senior%20HDFC%20Bank%20execs%20asked%20to%20leave%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774028433000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-07%2F04%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1751652135-1644.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdfc-bank-asks-three-senior-executives-to-leave-over-mis-selling-126032001172_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Move%20linked%20to%20alleged%20mis-selling%20of%20Credit%20Suisse%20AT1%20bonds%20to%20NRIs%3B%20comes%20days%20after%20chairman%20Atanu%20Chakraborty's%20sudden%20resignation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdfc-bank-asks-three-senior-executives-to-leave-over-mis-selling-1