0and%20latch%20the%20lid.%20That's%20it!%20I%20was%20initially%20skeptical%20that%20the%20latches%20would%20pop%20open%20during%20durability%20testing%2C%20but%20spoiler%20alert%2C%20they%20did%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20get%20very%20heavy.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20360-degree%20Hinomoto%20silent%20spinner%20wheels%20held%20up%20the%20trunk's%20weight%20without%20issue.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20trunks%20are%20meant%20to%20store%20your%20belongings%20for%20long%20trips%20and%20extended%20stays%2C%20so%20they%20get%20very%20heavy%20very%20quickly.%20It%20could%20be%20difficult%20for%20smaller%20people%20to%20maneuver%20and%20lift%20this%20bag%2C%20especially%20in%20tight%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298d721d5-a3f2-427b-a257-7f27baaa3334%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20extra%20space%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20extra%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20bag%20is%20designed%20to%20give%20you%20the%20most%20space.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20suitcases%20employ%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20features%20to%20offer%20extra%20space%2C%20typically%20by%20way%20of%20an%20expandable%20zipper%20or%20compression%20panels.%20This%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fredirect.viglink.com%2F%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.bagsmart.com%252Fproducts%252Fgetaway-24-check-in-side-opening%26key%3Da0a489b80c119e1fb25b8b4606294f7e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBagsmart%20Getaway%3C%2Fa%3E%20suitcase%20provides%20both%2C%20but%20takes%20it%20a%20step%20further.%20Instead%20of%20the%20traditional%20clamshell%20design%20like%20most%20hard%20suitcases%2C%20this%20one%20has%20a%20side%20opening%20where%20one%20half%20pops%20open%20like%20a%20trunk%2C%20held%20in%20place%20by%20suspension%20straps%20with%20a%20bridge%20lid%20design.%20Inside%2C%20in%20place%20of%20equally%20sized%20suitcase%20halves%2C%20there's%20a%2070%2F30%20split%2C%20which%20means%20one%20is%20a%20deep%20well%20for%20clothes%20and%20large%20it