me%20suitcases%20have%20just%20two%2C%20while%20others%20have%20four.%20A%20two-wheeled%20suitcase%20must%20be%20pulled%2C%20while%20a%20four-wheeled%20suitcase%20can%20be%20pushed%20or%20pulled%20in%20any%20direction.%20For%20that%20reason%2C%20a%20four-wheeled%20suitcase%20is%20our%20recommendation%2C%20as%20they%20glide%20easily%2C%20stand%20fully%20upright%2C%20and%20can%20navigate%20tight%20corners%20and%20many%20surfaces.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20two-wheeled%20bags%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20roll%20away%20on%20an%20incline%20or%20slippery%20flooring.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20have%20more%20packing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapacity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EChecked%20luggage%20usually%20comes%20in%20a%20medium%20or%20large%20size%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20ideal%20for%20a%20weeklong%20trip.%20Large%20checked%20bags%20are%20best%20for%20longer%20vacations%20or%20those%20who%20are%20prone%20to%20overpacking.%20Some%20suitcases%20split%20their%20capacity%20equally%20with%20two%20clamshells%2C%20while%20others%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fredirect.viglink.com%2F%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.bagsmart.com%252Fproducts%252Fgetaway-24-check-in-side-opening%26key%3Da0a489b80c119e1fb25b8b4606294f7e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBagsmart%20Getaway%20Check-in%3A%20Side-Opening%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fredirect.viglink.com%2F%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.carlfriedrik.com%252Fproducts%252Ftrunk%26key%3Da0a489b80c119e1fb25b8b4606294f7e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarl%20Friedrik%20Trunk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-72837-20%26h%3D3be1f0709ccec85fba2ae71f21dc8343ef547f9334d7802c3abb100997057ad0%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f431da%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftravel%252Fbest-checked-luggage%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.briggs-riley.com%252Fproducts%252Fmedium-expandable-spinner-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBriggs%20%26amp%3B%20Riley%20Medium%20Expandable%20Spinner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20utilize%20a%2070%2F30%20or%20an%2080%2F20%20split%20that%20instead%20has%20one%20large%20deep%20compartment%20and%20another%20smaller%20portion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20isn't%20better%20than%20the%20other%20%E2%80%94%20it%20really%20comes%20down%20to%20preference%20and%20the%20types%20of%20items%20you%20plan%20to%20pack.%20If%20I'm%20traveling%20for%20five%20to%20seven%20days%2C%20I'm%20more%20likely%20to%20choose%20a%20medium%20bag%20over%20a%20large%20one%2C%20and%20I%20might%20go%20with%20a%20traditional%20clamshell%20because%20I%20won't%20have%20as%20much%20stuff.%20For%20longer%20stints%2C%20I%20like%20deeper%20wells%20for%20better%20stacking%2C%20which%20I%20can%20then%20compress%20down%20with%20panels%20or%20straps%2C%20or%20open%20an%20expansion%20zipper.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20all%20those%20space-saving%20features%20can%20leave%20you%20vulnerable%20to%20overweight%20fees%20if%20you%20cram%20in%20too%20much.%20If%20that's%20a%20concern%2C%20go%20with%20a%20medium%20size%20checked%20bag%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20larger%2C%20heavier%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrganization%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20swear%20by%20packing%20cubes%20for%20staying%20organized%20on%20long%20trips%2C%20but%20sometimes%2C%20my%20suitcase%20still%20becomes%20a%20jumbled%20mess.%20Even%20when%20my%20clothes%20are%20organized%2C%20there%20are%20still%20loose%20items%20to%20consider%20such%20as%20shoes%2C%20toiletries%2C%20or%20small%20accessories.%20That's%20why%20I%20recommend%20a%20checked%20suitcase%20with%20built-in%20organization%20elements%20like%20pockets%2C%20pouches%2C%20or%20sleeves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20dimensions%20for%20checked%20suitcases%20may%20not%20be%20as%20heavily%20scrutinized%20as%20a%20carry-on%2C%20they're%20still%20important.%20If%20it's%20too%20large%2C%20you%20can%20be%20subject%20to%20oversized%20or%20overweight%20fees%2C%20and%20if%20it's%20too%20small%2C%20you%20might%20as%20well%20skip%20the%20baggage%20carousel%20and%20just%20take%20a%20carry-on.%20Each%20airline%20has%20their%20own%20rules%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20limits%2C%20but%20generally%2C%20most%20airlines%20cap%20checked%20luggage%20at%2062%20linear%20inches.%20That%20means%20the%20total%20length%2C%20width%2C%20and%20depth%20must%20equal%2062%20inches%20or%20less.%20Weight%20is%20also%20a%20consideration%2C%20as%20most%20airlines%20will%20charge%20a%20fee%20for%20any%20bag%20over%2050%20pounds.%20And%2C%20the%20larger%20the%20bag%2C%20the%20heavier%20it's%20likely%20to%20be%20when%20fully%20packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%20policies%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20we%20always%20hope%20a%20new%20suitcase%20will%20last%20for%20years%2C%20that's%20not%20always%20the%20case%2C%20either%20due%20to%20user%20error%20or%20a%20design%20malfunction.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20not%20only%20consider%20a%20generous%20return%20policy%20but%20also%20a%20good%20warranty.%20A%20warranty%20will%20cover%20unintended%20damage%20to%20zippers%20or%20wheels%2C%20faulty%20locks%2C%20or%20a%20cracked%20shell.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20even%20with%20brands%20offering%20a%20lifetime%20warranty%2C%20some%20situations%2C%20such%20as%20normal%20wear%20and%20tear%20or%20misuse%20may%20be%20excluded%20from%20the%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d19a3e6-ff43-429f-b560-075516c6303e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20the%20best%20checked%20luggage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20woman%20pulling%20an%20away%20suitcase%2C%20a%20woman%20tossing%20an%20antler%20suitcase%2C%20and%20a%20woman%20carrying%20a%20quince%20suitcase%20up%20the%20stairs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd74b0e98a37a4841f20c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20testing%20procedures%20including%20wheeling%20a%20fully%20packed%20bag%20on%20different%20terrain%2C%20tossing%20it%20on%20concrete%20five%20times%2C%20and%20carrying%20it%20up%20and%20down%20stairs.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Sabatini%2FBusiness%20Insider%3B%20Gabrielle%20Chase%2FBusiness%20Insider%3B%20Sally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213aecb77-efb0-4c7e-b36c-40ef09168fee%5C%22%3EOur%20testing%20methodology%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20single%20suitcase%20on%20this%20list%20was%20tested%20by%20a%20real%20traveler%20who%20filled%20their%20suitcase%20with%20an%20identical%20packing%20list%20and%20followed%20the%20same%20testing%20criteria.%20All%20picks%20listed%20here%20were%20selected%20based%20on%20their%20performance%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20test%20them%20in%20the%20future%20via%20our%20own%20travels.%20We%20tried%20a%20dozen%20suitcases%20during%20this%20round%20of%20testing%2C%20and%20we'll%20continually%20update%20this%20guide%20with%20new%20insights%20as%20we%20find%20new%20contenders.%20All%20suitcases%20followed%20our%20standard%20testing%20methodology%2C%20which%20considers%20packability%2C%20maneuverability%2C%20durability%2C%20price%20point%2C%20style%2C%20quality%20of%20materials%2C%20and%20added%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPacking%20list%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEach%20suitcase%20was%20packed%20with%20the%20same%20exact%20packing%20list%20of%20items%2C%20down%20to%20an%20exact%20number%20of%20shirts%20or%20underwear.%20The%20list%20was%20designed%20specifically%20to%20hold%20everything%20you%20might%20need%20on%20a%20weeklong%20vacation%2C%20including%20different%20types%20of%20clothes%2C%20toiletries%2C%20and%20shoes%20to%20represent%20a%20range%20of%20items%2C%20shapes%2C%20and%20weights.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20test%20the%20efficacy%20of%20each%20suitcase%2C%20every%20tester%20threw%20it%20repeatedly%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20five%20times%20to%20be%20exact%20%E2%80%94%20across%20a%20concrete%20surface%20to%20measure%20how%20it%20withstood%20or%20resisted%20damage%20and%20whether%20it%20resulted%20in%20scuffs%2C%20dents%2C%20or%20dings%20on%20the%20body%20or%20hardware.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EManeuverability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Once%20fully-packed%2C%20each%20bag%20was%20pushed%20and%20pulled%20across%20a%20variety%20of%20surfaces%20including%20carpet%2C%20wood%20or%20vinyl%20floors%2C%20pavement%2C%20concrete%2C%20and%20even%20grass%20to%20see%20how%20the%20wheels%20and%20handle%20would%20hold%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20used%20and%20fully%20tested%20all%20design%20features%2C%20including%20organization%20pockets%2C%20TSA-approved%20locks%2C%20expansion%20zippers%2C%20and%20the%20like.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a598311d-aa27-4ac0-9b41-cd657a980c7e%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20expert%20behind%20the%20guide%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2C%20freelance%20contributor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20the%20former%20Business%20Insider%20senior%20travel%20editor%20who%20specializes%20in%20covering%20all%20things%20travel.%20As%20a%20professional%20travel%20writer%2C%20I've%20tested%20dozens%20of%20suitcases%20in%20real-life%20settings%20ranging%20from%20carry-ons%20to%20duffels%2C%20backpacks%2C%20and%20checked%20bags%20of%20multiple%20sizes%20and%20designs.%20I%20tested%20multiple%20suitcases%20for%20this%20guide%20and%20designed%20the%20methodology%20based%20on%20my%20deep%20knowledge%20of%20product%20testing.%20I%20also%20combined%20my%20first-hand%20experience%20with%20BI's%20in-house%20testing%20team%20and%20their%20insights%20to%20round%20up%20the%20very%20best%20checked%20luggage%20choices%20for%20all%20types%20of%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220482ad49-f968-4d18-aef0-14f0b77dd280%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EBest%20checked%20luggage%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20I%20travel%20with%20a%20checked%20bag%20or%20a%20carry-on%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETSA%20guidelines%20often%20dictate%20the%20best%20answer%20here.%20For%20example%2C%20even%20the%20lightest%20packers%20will%20have%20to%20check%20a%20bag%20if%20they%20want%20to%20pack%20large%20liquids%20over%203.4%20ounces.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20your%20bag%20of%20choice%20exceeds%20carry-on%20approved%20measurements%2C%20it%20will%20need%20to%20be%20checked.%20Beyond%20that%2C%20for%20a%20weekend%20getaway%20or%20a%20trip%20under%20four%20days%2C%20a%20carry-on%20will%20suffice%2C%20while%20anything%20longer%20will%20usually%20warrant%20a%20checked%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20it%20hard-shell%20or%20soft-side%20luggage%20better%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20one%20comes%20down%20to%20personal%20preference.%20Hard%20suitcases%20are%20the%20lightest%2C%20and%20are%20most%20often%20made%20from%20virtually%20indestructible%20polycarbonate%2C%20while%20soft%20ones%20are%20typically%20heavier%20and%20constructed%20from%20ultra-durable%20nylon.%20In%20our%20experience%2C%20while%20hard%20shells%20provide%20adequate%20protection%2C%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20experience%20physical%20wear%20and%20tear%2C%20even%20after%20just%20a%20few%20trips.%20Soft-side%20bags%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20can%20be%20more%20durable%2C%20don't%20scuff%20as%20easily%2C%20and%20protect%20contents%20just%20as%20well.%20Either%20one%20from%20a%20reputable%20brand%20will%20do%20the%20job%2C%20but%20if%20you%20care%20deeply%20about%20physical%20appearance%20and%20keeping%20your%20suitcase%20looking%20as%20pristine%20as%20possible%2C%20we%20recommend%20a%20soft-sided%20suitcase.%20If%20you%20like%20a%20trendier%20look%20but%20don't%20mind%20a%20few%20scuffs%2C%20a%20hard%20shell%20is%20the%20way%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20most%20durable%20luggage%20for%20air%20travel%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20hard-shell%20bags%2C%20the%20most%20durable%20material%20is%20polycarbonate%20or%20aluminum.%20With%20soft-side%20luggage%2C%20look%20for%20high-strength%20nylon.%20In%20our%20experience%2C%20we've%20found%20these%20to%20be%20the%20most%20durable%20luggage%20materials%20for%20air%20travel%2C%20and%20they%20provide%20the%20same%20level%20of%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20should%20I%20avoid%20when%20buying%20luggage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20selecting%20checked%20luggage%2C%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20suitcase's%20weight%20when%20empty.%20If%20it's%20extra%20large%20or%20weighed%20down%20by%20features%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20stuck%20paying%20overweight%20fees.%20Also%20avoid%20materials%20that%20might%20damage%20easily%2C%20and%20check%20details%20like%20zippers%20and%20wheels%20to%20ensure%20they%20can%20hold%20up%20to%20heavy%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20clean%20checked%20luggage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20clean%20checked%20luggage%20on%20the%20outside%20is%20with%20either%20a%20magic%20eraser%20or%20a%20washcloth%20that%20can%20be%20dipped%20into%20mild%20soap%20and%20water.%20Both%20are%20effective%20at%20removing%20scuffs%2C%20dirt%2C%20and%20dust.%20For%20soft-sided%20luggage%2C%20you%20can%20also%20try%20spot%20cleaning%20with%20a%20fabric%20cleaner.%20To%20clean%20the%20inside%2C%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-handheld-vacuum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehandheld%20vacuum%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20remove%20dirt%20and%20debris%2C%20spot%20treat%20any%20stains%2C%20try%20baking%20soda%20to%20remove%20odors%2C%20and%20always%20air%20dry%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20maximum%20weight%20of%20checked%20luggage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20all%20airlines%20enforce%20their%20own%20rules%2C%20most%20limit%20each%20piece%20of%20checked%20luggage%20to%2050%20pounds%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20items%20are%20not%20allowed%20in%20checked%20luggage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20dangerous%20items%20are%20never%20allowed%20within%20checked%20luggage%2C%20such%20as%20flammable%20items%20like%20lithium%20batteries%2C%20explosives%2C%20and%20some%20firearms.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20check%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tsa.gov%2Ftravel%2Fsecurity-screening%2Fwhatcanibring%2Fall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20full%20list%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20what%20is%20permitted%20and%20forbidden%20according%20to%20TSA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20checked%20bag%20and%20a%20trunk%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20between%20a%20checked%20bag%20and%20a%20trunk%20relates%20to%20its%20shape%2C%20depth%2C%20and%20the%20way%20it%20opens.%20Standard%20checked%20suitcases%20usually%20open%20clamshell-style%20down%20the%20middle%20with%20two%20equally%20sized%20compartments%2C%20while%20trunks%20open%20with%20a%20hinged%20lid%20and%20usually%20have%20one%20main%20space%20for%20packing%20instead%20of%20two.%20Trunks%20may%20also%20be%20larger%2C%20and%20therefore%20heavier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-checked-luggage%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774027989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd849058b5806618e7cd50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-checked-luggage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20checked%20luggage%20is%20roomy%20and%20durable.%20After%20testing%20a%20dozen%20bags%2C%20our%20picks%20include%20hard-shell%2C%20soft-side%2C%20lightweight%2C%20and%20luxury%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehochberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Emily%20Hochberg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-checked-luggage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22