%20continues%20%E2%80%94%20just%20within%20a%20clearly%20defined%20band.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeale%20Mahoney%20-%20Spiking%20Gasoline%20Prices%20May%20Wipe%20Out%20Larger%20Tax%20Refunds%20Touted%20by%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMahoney%2C%20a%20Stanford%20University%20economist%2C%20recently%20joined%20three%20of%20his%20colleagues%20from%20the%20Stanford%20Institute%20for%20Economic%20Policymaking%20(SIEPR)%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnealemahoney.substack.com%2Fp%2Fspiking-gasoline-prices-may-wipe%3Fmod%3Ddjem_mwnneedtoknow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereveal%20the%20results%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20recent%20study%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20this%20year's%20tax%20refunds%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20erased%20by%20surging%20gas%20prices%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Iran%20war.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFellow%20Stanford%20researchers%20Ryan%20Commings%2C%20Caleb%20Brobst%2C%20and%20former%20White%20House%20economic%20advisor%20Jared%20Bernstein%20concluded%20that%20despite%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20promises%20of%20more%20robust%20tax%20returns%20and%20savings%20this%20year%2C%20most%20families%20will%20be%20paying%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20tax%20at%20the%20pump.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20U.S.%20launched%20military%20operations%20against%20Iran%20on%20February%2028%2C%20gasoline%20prices%20have%20risen%20by%2081%20cents%20per%20gallon%2C%20from%20%242.98%20to%20%243.79%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysis%20noted.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20typical%20family%2C%20the%20higher%20prices%20will%20take%20a%20meaningful%20bite%20out%20of%20their%20budget%2C%20costing%20them%20an%20extra%20%2468%20this%20month.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaymond%20James'%20institutional%20equity%20strategist%2C%20Tavis%20McCourt%2C%20recently%20made%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-tax-refunds-trump-big-beautiful-bill-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimilar%20argum