g%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E's%20view%20that%20he%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20alarmed%26quot%3B%20if%20an%20engineer%20being%20paid%20%24500%2C000%20didn't%20use%20AI%20tokens%20equivalent%20to%20at%20least%20half%20of%20that%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20%24500%2C000%20engineer%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20ask%20them%20how%20much%20did%20you%20spend%20in%20tokens%3F%20If%20that%20person%20said%20%245%2C000%2C%20I%20will%20go%20ape%20something%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20published%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevie%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20underlying%20concept%20and%20trend%20is%20going%20to%20be%20very%20real%2C%20because%20workers%20who%20properly%20leverage%20AI%20are%20only%20going%20to%20consume%20more%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20compute%20budgets%20are%20just%20going%20to%20monotonically%20go%20up%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20won't%20just%20be%20workers%20either%2C%20Levie%20said.%20Agents%2C%20which%20can%20run%20during%20all%20hours%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20token%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20aren't%20chatbot%20workflows%20answering%20a%20simple%20question%2C%20but%20agents%20that%20are%20running%20and%20processing%20through%20incredible%20amounts%20of%20data%20at%20scale%2C%20and%20generating%20all%20new%20forms%20of%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20will%20be%20thrilled%20with%20their%20AI%20compute%20budgets.%20Venture%20capitalist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchamath-palihapitiya-ai-costs-tokens-8090-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChamath%20Palihapitiya%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20had%20to%20tell%208090%2C%20his%20startup%20software%20company%2C%20to%20stop%20using%20Cursor%2C%20a%20popular%20AI%20coding%20tool%2C%20after%20s