pack%2C%20the%20largest%20one%20I%20own%2C%20to%20hold%20everything%20I%20brought.%20I%20packed%20my%20work%20computer%2C%20camera%2C%20and%20chargers%3B%20my%20tripod%2C%20toiletries%2C%20and%20medications%3B%20one%20packing%20cube%20stuffed%20with%20clothing%3B%20and%20additional%20necessities%2C%20like%20a%20raincoat%2C%20a%20tote%2C%20and%20a%20pair%20of%20comfy%20shoes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I%20did%20pretty%20well%20for%20my%20first%20time%20packing%20this%20light%2C%20but%20I%20missed%20a%20handful%20of%20items.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20I%20packed%20was%20laundry%20sheets%20so%20I%20could%20wash%20my%20clothes%20every%20couple%20of%20days.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Green%20and%20floral%20clothing%20being%20washed%20with%20soapy%20water%20in%20a%20bathroom%20sink.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6303f502c2794d00197f1603%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELaundry%20sheets%20are%20small%2C%20dry%2C%20scented%20squares%20that%20look%20like%20dryer%20sheets%2C%20but%20they're%20actually%20pads%20of%20laundry%20detergent%20that%20turn%20into%20a%20bubbly%20soap%20when%20mixed%20with%20water.%20They're%20great%20for%20on-the-go%20use%2C%20and%20I%20like%20to%20pack%20them%20when%20traveling%20so%20I%20can%20do%20my%20own%20laundry%20in%20sinks%20and%20then%20air-dry%20my%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20came%20prepared%20so%20I%20could%20pack%20fewer%20clothes%20without%20spending%20time%20and%20money%20at%20a%20laundromat.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELaundry%20sheets%20allowed%20me%20to%20pack%20fewer%20outfits%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20I'd%20brought%20more%20socks%20because%20they%20took%20longer%20to%20air-dry%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20clothes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%