er.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20one%20packing%20cube%20to%20stuff%20all%20my%20clothing%20into%2C%20and%20it%20took%20up%20less%20space%20in%20the%20bag%20by%20keeping%20it%20compact.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'm%20also%20glad%20I%20packed%20a%20tote%20bag%20to%20keep%20some%20items%20separate%20and%20easier%20to%20access%20during%20my%20travels%2C%20like%20my%20phone%2C%20wallet%2C%20and%20headphones.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tote%20bag%20on%20a%20train%20seat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6303f4fcc2794d00197f1600%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20travel%20days%2C%20I%20used%20the%20tote%20to%20separate%20and%20hold%20personal%20belongings%20I'd%20want%20to%20use%20on%20trains%20or%20buses%20so%20that%20I%20could%20stuff%20my%20backpack%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverhead-bin-space-not-guaranteed-to-passengers-flying-economy-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoverhead%20bin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20quickly%20find%20items%20I%20needed%2C%20such%20as%20my%20headphones%2C%20and%20also%20kept%20my%20bulky%20backpack%20out%20of%20the%20way.%20By%20stowing%20my%20backpack%20on%20the%20shelf%20above%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20maximize%20leg%20room%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20I%20wish%20I'd%20remembered%20to%20bring%20a%20portable%20charging%20battery%20for%20long%20days%20of%20exploring%20when%20my%20phone%20nearly%20died.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224806%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ski%20trip%20packing%20regrets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63062583c9a2da0018095b14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223605%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20portable%20charger%20would've%20worked%20wonders%20on%20this%20trip.%3Cp%3EF.J.%20Jimenez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%2C%20I%20was%20out%20of%20my%20hotel%20room%20for%2012%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20not%20every%20train%20I%20rode%20had%20an%20outlet.%20During%20these%20times%2C%20I%20had%20to%20use%20my%20phone%20less%20to%20conserve%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20was%20traveling%20solo%2C%20I%20couldn't%20risk%20letting%20my%20phone%20die%20for%20safety%20reasons.%20But%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20brought%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-battery-packs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eportable%20battery%20pack%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20I%20could%20have%20used%20my%20phone%20as%20much%20as%20needed%20to%20snap%20extra%20pictures%20or%20take%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20those%20long%20days%20of%20exploring%2C%20I'm%20glad%20I%20packed%20Mio%2C%20a%20caffeinated%2C%20fruity%20addition%20to%20water%20that%20also%20packs%20in%20B%20vitamins.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20a%20mio%20energy%20bottle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63062783c9a2da0018095ba7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summertime%2C%20I%20drink%20Mio%20every%20morning%2C%20a%20caffeinated%20fruit-flavored%20addition%20to%20water%20with%20B%20vitamins.%20I%20can't%20stand%20drinking%20hot%20coffee%20in%20the%20heat%2C%20and%20I%20find%20it%20gives%20me%20the%20extra%20jolt%20of%20energy%20I%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20visited%20Canada%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20I%20brought%20my%20Mio%2C%20and%20it%20helped%20me%20feel%20comfortable%20and%20alert%20while%20on%20the%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20thought%20it%20would%20have%20been%20nice%20to%20pack%20some%20tea%