shareholder%20letter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm%20offered%20a%20look%20at%20how%20it's%20applying%20AI%20across%20operations%20and%20workflows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20also%20flagged%20the%20biggest%20risks%20to%20a%20successful%20rollout%2C%20including%20attracting%20and%20keeping%20talent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20is%20pushing%20deeper%20into%20artificial%20intelligence%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20it%20could%20mean%20for%20the%20firm's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202025%20shareholder%20letter%2C%20released%20Friday%2C%20Goldman's%20leaders%20doubled%20down%20on%20their%20priorities%20tied%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-job-cuts-ai-operations-overhaul-onegs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecent%20refresh%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20%26quot%3BOne%20Goldman%20Sachs%26quot%3B%20initiative%20to%20streamline%20the%20bank's%20services%20and%20boost%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20described%20One%20GS%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20operating%20model%20propelled%20by%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehighlighted%20six%20areas%20%26quot%3Bripe%20for%20disruption%26quot%3B%3A%20client%20onboarding%20and%20KYC%2C%20vendor%20management%2C%20regulatory%20reporting%2C%20lending%2C%20enterprise%20risk%20management%2C%20and%20sales%20enablement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20doesn't%20just%20mean%20retooling%20our%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20taking%20a%20front-to-back%20view%20of%20how%20we%20organize%20our%20people%2C%20make%20decisions%2C%20and%20think%20about%20productivity%2C%20efficiency%2C%20and%20resilience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-layoffs-cuts-underperformers-sra-spring-summer-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%3C%2Fa%3E%20signaled%20that%20executing%20on%20its%20AI%20ambitions%20will%20depend%20heavily%20on%20talent%2C%20where%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-cfo-banker-talent-ma-wave-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebattle%20continues%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20unfold%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-ai-technologists-talent-hiring-boom-salaries-influence-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enab%20top%20performers%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%20from%20within%20the%20financial%20services%20industry%20and%20from%20businesses%20outside%20the%20financial%20services%20industry%2C%20including%20the%20technology%20industry%2C%20for%20qualified%20employees%20has%20often%20been%20intense%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%20increased%20competition%20in%20hiring%20and%20retaining%20employees%26quot%3B%20tied%20to%20its%20technology%20initiatives%20and%20newer%20business%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20pressure%20is%20particularly%20acute%20in%20newer%20hubs%20central%20to%20Goldman's%20operating%20model.%20The%20bank%20said%2045%25%20of%20its%20workforce%20is%20now%20based%20in%20strategic%20locations%20like%20Warsaw%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20Salt%20Lake%20City.%20In%20those%20markets%2C%20Goldman%20often%20competes%20with%20firms%20that%20have%20a%20deeper%20local%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20firm%20continues%20to%20draw%20significant%20interest%20from%20candidates.%20Goldman%20said%20it%20received%20more%20than%20one%20million%20experienced%20hire%20applications%20in%202025%2C%20up%2033%25%20from%20the%20prior%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226cadb653-5d55-444a-a4de-5ae6a099f3d9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20biggest%20risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20shedding%20some%20light%20on%20its%20future%20AI%20bets%2C%20Goldman%20also%20explained%20what%20it%20sees%20as%20the%20biggest%20risks%20tied%20to%20its%20use%20of%20the%20technology%20that%20it%20believes%20shareholders%20ought%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20environment%20relating%20to%20AI%20is%20uncertain%20and%20rapidly%20evolving%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20that%20AI%20models%20may%20generate%20incorrect%20outputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-elite-business-schools-wharton-overhauling-curriculum-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGenerative%20AI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20firm%20flagged%2C%20are%20prone%20to%20making%20mistakes%2C%20which%20could%2C%20in%20a%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20%26quot%3Bresult%20in%20the%20release%20of%20private%2C%20confidential%20or%20proprietary%20information%2C%20that%20reflect%20biases%20included%20in%20the%20data%26quot%3B%20they're%20trained%20on.%20And%20it%20pointed%20to%20its%20use%20of%20%26quot%3BAI%20models%20developed%20by%20third%20parties%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20firm%20said%20makes%20it%20%26quot%3Bdependent%26quot%3B%20on%20how%20those%20providers%20build%20their%20models.%20What's%20more%2C%20bad%20actors%20could%20harness%20AI's%20capabilities%20%26quot%3Bto%20commit%20fraud%20and%20misappropriate%20funds%20and%20to%20facilitate%20cyber%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20struck%20a%20bullish%20tone%20in%20the%20letter%20about%20his%20prognosis%20for%20AI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20this%20technology%20is%20going%20to%20reshape%20the%20way%20we%20live%20and%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20are%20significant%20questions%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20mind-bending%20speed%20of%20its%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20any%20new%20technology%2C%20there%20will%20be%20winners%20and%20losers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20added.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20there%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20periods%20of%20recalibration%2C%20in%20the%20long%20run%20I%20believe%20the%20net%20benefits%20from%20AI%20will%20accrue%20to%20many%20institutions%20as%20AI%20investment%20continues%20to%20build.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20been%20a%20central%20focus%20for%20Solomon.%20The%20bank%20has%20partnered%20with%20developers%20like%20Cognition%20Labs%20to%20create%20unique%20products%20and%20rolled%20out%20its%20GS%20AI%20chatbot%20to%20its%20more%20than%2047%2C000%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20conference%20in%20Europe%20last%20year%2C%20he%20said%20he%20wished%20Goldman%20could%20spend%20more%20than%20its%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-ceo-david-solomon-ai-headcount-investment-spending-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%246%20billion%20technology%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20noted%20at%20the%20time%20that%20investment%20levels%20were%20somewhat%20constrained%20by%20the%20need%20to%20deliver%20shareholder%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-lays-out-ai-ambitions-biggest-risks-shareholder-letter-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774023058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd82955b58f1f0f9335a71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-lays-out-ai-ambitions-biggest-risks-shareholder-letter-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20new%20shareholder%20letter%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20leaders%20offered%20insight%20into%20how%20the%20bank%20is%20navigating%20the%20competitive%20AI%20revolution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ralexander%40insider.com%20(Reed%20Alexander)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-lays-out-ai-ambitions-biggest-risks-shareholder-letter-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20a%20chief%20innovation%20officer%2C%20writing%20fiction%20helps%20me%20with%20my%20job.%20I'm%20now%20a%20better%20strategist.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roopa%20Unnikrishnan%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aef07bfd4fbd083f29c394%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20shares%20how%20writing%20fiction%20has%20made%20her%20better%20at%20her%209-to-5%20job.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFiction%20writing%20builds%20the%20scenario-planning%20muscles%20AI%20can't%20replicate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20novelist's%20research%20discipline%20outperforms%20a%20slide%20deck's%20worth%20of%20analysis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECreative%20imagination%20is%20a%20strategic%20asset%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20soft%20skill.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20I%20shook%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-you-are-a-great-leader-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrategy%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20of%20her%20deeply%20held%20convictions%20by%20asking%20three%20questions%20that%20made%20her%20stop%20and%20think.%20It%20shifted%20the%20tenor%20of%20the%20discussion%2C%20and%20after%20a%20more%20expansive%2C%20free-flowing%20exchange%2C%20she%20asked%20me%20how%20I%20find%20new%20ways%20to%20address%20complex%20issues.%20The%20answer%20surprised%20her%3A%20I%20think%20and%20ask%20questions%20like%20a%20writer.%20I%20didn't%20become%20a%20sharper%20strategist%20by%20filling%20my%20calendar%20with%20training%20courses%20or%20innovation%20workshops.%20I%20became%20sharper%20by%20writing%20fiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20believe%20this%20is%20a%20skill%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Finterpersonal-therapy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emental%20framework%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20keep%20strategists%20and%20innovators%20relevant%20in%20an%20AI%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c31da16a-9c6e-4952-a293-45384d919e0c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20fiction%20rewired%20my%20strategy%20brain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20loved%20writing.%20I've%20written%20creatively%20and%20cooking%20blogs%2C%20poetry%2C%20and%20business%20books%20and%20articles.%20But%20the%20turning%20point%20came%20during%20COVID%2C%20on%20long%20Zoom%20calls%20with%20my%20parents.%20Those%20conversations%2C%20full%20of%20half-remembered%20details%20about%201960s%20South%20India%2C%20nudged%20me%20from%20business%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-book-30-days-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewriting%20into%20fiction%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20novel%20grew%20from%20those%20calls%2C%20but%20so%20did%20something%20else%3A%20a%20different%20way%20of%20thinking%20about%20complex%20problems%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20that%20book%20work%20on%20the%20page%2C%20I%20couldn't%20just%20%26quot%3Bbe%20creative.%26quot%3B%20I%20had%20to%20be%20precise.%20I%20spent%20hours%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-interview-their-grandparents-to-create-holiday-memories-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterviewing%20my%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20combing%20through%20archival%20materials%2C%20and%20cross-checking%20geography%2C%20politics%2C%20cultural%20norms%2C%20news%20events%2C%20and%20police%20procedures%20for%20that%20era%20and%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20uncannily%20like%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-industry-outlook-entry-level-workers-hiring-mckinsey-bcg-bain-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearly%20consulting%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20stretched%20over%20an%20entire%20world%20rather%20than%20a%20single%20client%20issue.%20In%20my%20day%20job%2C%20that%20same%20discipline%20shows%20up%20when%20I'm%20parachuting%20into%20a%20new%20business%20at%20Pfizer%2C%20or%20navigating%20the%20integration%20of%20a%20new%20technology%20at%20Harman%20or%20Vontier%2C%20or%20framing%20growth%20bets%20at%20IDEX.%20I'm%20still%20mapping%20stakeholders%2C%20rules%2C%20and%20constraints%20%E2%80%94%20but%20fiction%20trained%20me%20to%20hold%20a%20whole%20ecosystem%20in%20my%20head%2C%20not%20just%20a%20slide's%20worth%20of%20bullet%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20often%20challenged%20by%20folks%20who%20say%20AI%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%20initial%20research%20and%20increasingly%20generate%20ideas.%20The%20difference%20is%20that%20the%20human%20mind%20inherently%20understands%20the%20uncanny%20valley%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-advertising-controversies-flops-coca-cola-mcdonalds-meta-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-generated%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20thinking%26quot%3B%20and%20rejects%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeuroscience%20gives%20language%20to%20what%20I%20sensed%20was%20happening.%20Writing%20activates%20the%20brain's%20default%20network%2C%20which%20supports%20our%20ability%20to%20simulate%20hypothetical%20scenes%2C%20spaces%2C%20and%20mental%20states.%20I%20feel%20that%20every%20time%20I%20sit%20down%20to%20sketch%20a%20chapter%2C%20I'm%20running%20scenario-planning%20drills%2C%20just%20with%20characters%20instead%20of%20cost%20centers.%20Reading%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-published-bestseller-first-book-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewriting%20fiction%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20my%20way%20of%20exercising%20the%20same%20circuitry%20I%20rely%20on%20to%20anticipate%20market%20reactions%2C%20understand%20stakeholder%20perspectives%2C%20and%20work%20through%20organizational%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b17bde2-521f-4b75-ab71-a40bf60330ef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20to%20research%20entire%20worlds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20surprise%20you%20to%20know%20that%20the%20research%20standard%20for%20serious%20fiction%20is%20brutal%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20best%20way.%20For%20The%20Jasmine%20Murders%2C%20I%20couldn't%20hide%20behind%20%26quot%3Bclose%20enough.%26quot%3B%20And%20ChatGPT%2C%20Perplexity%2C%20and%20their%20ilk%2C%20despite%20the%20rivers%20of%20water%20they%20use%20in%20their%20research%2C%20often%20settle%20for%20%26quot%3Bclose%20enough.%26quot%3B%20Not%20so%20for%20the%20human%20fiction%20writer.%20If%20a%20train%20line%20didn't%20exist%20in%201965%2C%20it%20couldn't%20exist%20in%20my%20plot.%20If%20a%20particular%20police%20procedure%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20I%20had%20to%20find%20another%20way%20to%20get%20my%20character%20in%20or%20out%20of%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20experience%20sharpened%20the%20muscles%20I%20use%20constantly%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-21-ad-execs-that-wield-the-most-power-over-facebook-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echief%20strategy%20and%20innovation%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20stamina%20to%20stay%20with%20a%20question%20long%20after%20the%20first%20answer%20appears.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20instinct%20to%20check%20not%20just%20one%20source%20but%20many%E2%80%94and%20notice%20the%20gaps%20between%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20habit%20of%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20am%20I%20not%20seeing%20in%20this%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20I%20have%20enough%20to%20make%20a%20slide%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20work%2C%20when%20I%20walk%20into%20a%20review%20now%2C%20I'm%20not%20just%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20market%20size%3F%26quot%3B%20I'm%20thinking%20like%20a%20novelist%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20rules%20govern%20this%20world%3F%20Who%20has%20power%3F%20What%20invisible%20norms%20are%20shaping%20behavior%3F%20What%20would%20break%20if%20we%20changed%20one%20thing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220085e2e5-225a-4266-87e3-3c65074fc955%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20use%20the%20same%20toolkit%20from%20page%20to%20boardroom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20I've%20stopped%20seeing%20a%20boundary%20between%20%26quot%3Bmy%20writing%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmy%20strategy%20life.%26quot%3B%20The%20toolkits%20are%20almost%20identical%3B%20only%20the%20stakes%20and%20vocabularies%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20the%20overlap%20looks%20from%20my%20seat%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EResearch%20and%20synthesis.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20I%20dive%20into%201960s%20South%20Indian%20police%20procedures%2C%20I'm%20doing%20what%20I%20did%20when%20walking%20into%20an%20unfamiliar%20industry%20or%20a%20new%20vertical%20I%20rapidly%20building%20domain%20knowledge%2C%20triangulating%20sources%2C%20and%20boiling%20chaos%20into%20a%20coherent%20narrative.%20AI%20can%20help%20with%20an%20initial%20scan%2C%20but%20primary%20research%20in%20the%20form%20of%20archival%20review%20and%20interviews%20is%20critical%20to%20develop%20deep%20insight.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPattern%20recognition.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Creating%20believable%20characters%20forced%20me%20to%20notice%20patterns%20in%20behavior%2C%20motivation%2C%20and%20social%20dynamics.%20Those%20same%20instincts%20help%20me%20read%20organizational%20culture%2C%20competitive%20moves%2C%20and%20market%20signals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EScenario%20development.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Every%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20if%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20ask%20on%20the%20page%E2%80%94Would%20she%20plausibly%20do%20this%3F%20Would%20that%20consequence%20follow%3F%E2%80%94is%20a%20rehearsal%20for%20the%20stress%20tests%20I%20run%20on%20strategic%20options.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStorytelling.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Board%20decks%20and%20town%20halls%20land%20very%20differently%20when%20they're%20built%20like%20narratives%20rather%20than%20data%20dumps.%20My%20years%20of%20revising%20scenes%20have%20shown%20up%20in%20how%20I%20frame%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20in%20ambiguity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20rarely%20know%20how%20a%20novel%20will%20truly%20land%20until%20the%20last%20pages%20click%20into%20place.%20That%20same%20tolerance%20for%20not%20knowing%20helps%20when%20markets%20shift%20mid-plan%20or%20an%20acquisition%20takes%20an%20unexpected%20turn.%20Fiction%20normalized%20for%20me%20that%20good%20outcomes%20can%20emerge%20from%20messy%2C%20nonlinear%20paths.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20I%20wrote%2C%20the%20more%20I%20noticed%20my%20default%20mode%20in%20meetings%20shifting.%20Instead%20of%20jumping%20to%20a%20solution%2C%20I'd%20find%20myself%20asking%20questions%20a%20novelist%20would%20ask%3A%20%26quot%3BWhose%20story%20is%20this%3F%20What's%20unsaid%20here%3F%20What's%20the%20scene%20behind%20the%20numbers%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20answers%20often%20surfaced%20risks%20or%20opportunities%20we'd%20otherwise%20have%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c422700-37b2-40eb-b59d-f1b030ef0a76%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20rigor%20and%20imagination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20single%20most%20valuable%20habit%20fiction%20has%20given%20me%20is%20learning%20to%20live%20in%20the%20tension%20between%20fact%20and%20possibility.%20There%20are%20very%20useful%20AI%20tools%20out%20there%20that%20can%20help%20create%20foundational%20information%20and%20drafts%2C%20but%20it%20is%20you%2C%20the%20human%2C%20who%20will%20extract%20the%20unique%20ideas%20and%20pathways%20that%20drive%20distinctive%20courses%20of%20action%20and%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20write%20a%20mystery%20set%20in%201960s%20South%20India%2C%20there%20are%20hard%20constraints%3A%20the%20maps%2C%20the%20politics%2C%20the%20social%20norms%2C%20the%20technology%2C%20the%20procedures.%20Within%20those%20constraints%2C%20I'm%20free%20to%20invent%20characters%2C%20twists%2C%20and%20themes.%20If%20I%20ignore%20the%20facts%2C%20the%20story%20rings%20false.%20If%20I%20only%20recite%20the%20facts%2C%20there%20is%20no%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20balance%20is%20exactly%20what%20strategic%20work%20has%20demanded%20of%20me..%20The%20market%20data%2C%20regulatory%20boundaries%2C%20and%20operational%20realities%20are%20non-negotiable.%20Inside%20them%2C%20there%20is%20still%20enormous%20room%20to%20imagine%20different%20futures.%20The%20best%20answers%20I've%20seen%E2%80%94whether%20around%20portfolio%20bets%2C%20M%26amp%3BA%20theses%2C%20or%20innovation%20pipelines%E2%80%94have%20come%20from%20holding%20both%20truths%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Froopaonline.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoopa%20Unnikrishnan%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20the%20author%20of%20The%20Career%20Catapult%20and%20has%20a%20book%20on%20strategy%20in%20an%20uncertain%20world%20coming%20out%20in%202027.%20Her%20fiction%20debut%2C%20The%20Jasmine%20Murders%2C%20launched%20to%20acclaim%20in%20India%20in%20January%202026.%20She%20was%20most%20recently%20the%20SVP%2C%20Chief%20Strategy%20%26amp%3B%20Innovation%20Officer%20of%20IDEX%20Corporation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-writing-fiction-made-me-a-better-business-strategist-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774022941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aef07bfd4fbd083f29c394%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-writing-fiction-made-me-a-better-business-strategist-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Writing%20fiction%20sharpened%20my%20strategic%20thinking%20in%20ways%20no%20workshop%20could%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20how%20I%20use%20a%20novelist's%20mindset%20to%20solve%20complex%20business%20problems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Roopa%20Unnikrishnan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-writing-fictio