20who%20have%20been%20working%20day%20and%20night%20to%20help%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harmeet%20shares.%20He%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20an%20elderly%20man%20whom%20they%20recently%20rescued.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20lost%20everything%20in%20the%20flood%20water%2C%20but%20soon%20after%20he%20was%20on%20the%20boat%20with%20us%2C%20he%20asked%20for%20a%20life%20jacket%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20will%20come%20and%20help%20your%20team%20rescue%20others%20who%20are%20stuck.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Botas%20are%20being%20deployed%20to%20perform%20rescue%20operations%20in%20flood%20affected%20Punjab%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496955%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBotas%20are%20being%20deployed%20to%20perform%20rescue%20operations%20in%20flood-affected%20Punjab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20disaster%20and%20deployed%20the%20NDRF%2C%20SDRF%2C%20Army%2C%20Air%20Force%2C%20BSF%2C%20and%20police.%20Evacuations%20and%20food%